FBIS4-54767 "dreeu087__a94012" FBIS-EEU-94-087-A Daily Report 4 May 1994 ANNEX Czech Republic Government Approves Attorney General Appointment Government Approves Attorney General Appointment AU0405171094 Prague CTK in English 1448 GMT 4 May 94 -- FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY AU0405171094 Prague CTK English BFN [Text] Prague, May 4 (CTK) -- The Czech Government today unanimously approved Bohumira Kopecna into the post of the Czech attorney general, Prime Minister Vaclav Klaus told journalists after the government session. The government is glad that a woman will hold a more significant post in the state administration, Klaus added. Kopecna has so far been heading the Attorney General's Office as deputy attorney general.
